<div id="greeting">
  <img src="<%= @current_user.avatar_url %>&size=40">
  <br>Hello, <strong><%= @current_user.nickname %></strong>
</div>

<div id="map-wrapper" class="box">
  <form action="/" method="GET">
    Please map
    <br><span><%= @current_user.nickname %>.ruhoh.com </span>
    <br>to
    <br>http://<input type="text" value="<%= @mapping.domain %>" name="domain">/
    <br><button type="submit" name="submit">Update</button>
  </form>
</div>

<div class="box" style="text-align:center">
  <h3>Change Your Domain's DNS Records</h3>
  <p>
    In the interest of speed, I'm going to link to GitHub's wonderful 
    tutorial for configuring your domain's DNS records.</a>
    <br><a href="https://help.github.com/articles/setting-up-a-custom-domain-with-pages">setting-up-a-custom-domain</a>
    <br><small>You only need to follow the directions after "Setting up DNS"</small>
  </p>
  <p style="color:red">Be sure to use the ruhoh specific values below:</p>

  <h4>Toplevel Domain (TLD)</h4>
  <label>A Record</label> <input type="text" value="50.116.20.239" READONLY>

  
  <h4>Subdomains</h4>
  <label>CNAME</label> <input type="text" value="<%= @current_user.nickname %>.ruhoh.com" READONLY>
</div>
